THE HUMBLE umbrella has had a 21st century makeover.With many parts of Mzansi experiencing much-needed rain, the Opus One umbrella could come in handy.Opus One is fitted with an LED light which flashes red when it&rsquo;s going to rain.All you have to do is shake the handle!But how does it know it&rsquo;s going to rain? The so-called &ldquo;smart umbrella&rdquo; uses bluetooth to connect to your smart phone, where it gets an updated weather report. If rain is forecast for your area, it will warn you!The umbrella will also ensure you never leave home without your cellphone, as it will vibrate when it is too far from the phone. It&rsquo;s already available in Japan and Korea.